*{{cite book | title= Zbornik Matice srpske za knji<U+017E>evnost i jezik | author= Matica srpska | url= http://books.google.com/books?id=WhM_AQAAIAAJ | year= 1965 | isbn= | publisher= Matica srpska | location= Novi Sad | quote= <U+0420><U+0443><U+0441><U+043A><U+0438> <U+043B><U+0435><U+0442><U+043E><U+043F><U+0438><U+0441><U+0438> <U+0438><U+043C><U+0430>]<U+0443> <U+0431><U+0435><U+043B><U+0435><U+0448><U+043A><U+0443> <U+0434><U+0430> ]<U+0435> <U+0441><U+0440><U+043F><U+0441><U+043A><U+0438> <U+043C><U+043E><U+043D><U+0430><U+0445> <U+041B><U+0430><U+0437><U+0430><U+0440> <U+0441><U+0430> <U+0421><U+044C>. <U+0413><U+043E><U+0440><U+0435> 1404. <U+0433><U+043E><U+0434>. <U+043D><U+0430><U+043C><U+0435><U+0441><U+0442><U+0438><U+043E> <U+0447><U+0430><U+0441><U+043E><U+0432><U+043D><U+0438><U+043A> <U+043D><U+0430> <U+0434><U+0432><U+043E><U+0440><U+0446><U+0443> <U+0440><U+0443><U+0441><U+043A><U+043E><U+0433> <U+0432><U+0435><U+043B><U+0438><U+043A><U+043E><U+0433> <U+043A><U+043D><U+0435><U+0437><U+0430> <U+0443> <U+041C><U+043E><U+0441><U+043A><U+0432><U+043F>. <U+201E><U+0421><U+0432><U+0430><U+043A><U+043E><U+0433><U+0430> <U+0447><U+0430><U+0441><U+0430> ...|ref=harv}}

